name: The Disappearance of Natalee Holloway
overview: A man searches for answers about his daughter's mysterious disappearance from Aruba in 2005.

episodes.name: New Lead
episodes.overview: Dave Holloway, the father of Natalee Holloway—who disappeared in Aruba in 2005 while on a high-school graduation trip—pursues a new lead in the premiere of the true-crime series.

episodes.name: The Sting
episodes.overview: Pursuing a lead that may shed light on his daughter’s disappearance, Dave Holloway and a team of investigators dive into a covert operation. The goal: obtain a taped confession, and evidence that could convict his daughter’s killer.

episodes.name: The Sting: Day 2
episodes.overview: Tensions are high as the sting operation in New Orleans continues. The investigative team is running out of time to obtain the necessary information from the co-conspirator regarding his involvement in the Natalee Holloway case.

episodes.name: Aruba
episodes.overview: TJ and his team head to Aruba to begin phase two of their investigation – attempting to obtain DNA evidence from Natalee’s alleged burial site. Dave must convince his informant to go the extra mile to ensure the next step of their investigation.

episodes.name: The Burial Site
episodes.overview: TJ races to the location that the co-conspirator claims is where he dug up Natalee's remains in 2010.  Working with the Aruban authorities, they search for DNA that could lead to convicting those involved in Natalee’s disappearance.
